# AI Document Analyzer

A command-line AI pipeline that analyzes any technical text 
and produces a structured intelligent report.

## What It Produces

- Summary — concise 100 word compression
- Key Concepts — 5 technical concepts extracted as JSON
- Q&A Pairs — 3 questions that test deep understanding
- Personalized Explanation — adapts to beginner, 
  intermediate, or expert level
- Cost Report — exact token usage and API cost

## Technical Highlights

- Prompt chaining — 4 steps, each builds on the last
- Dynamic prompts — output adapts to user expertise level
- Input sanitization — injection defense before any LLM call
- Token cost tracking — across all pipeline steps
- Error handling — each step fails independently

## Setup

pip install -r requirements.txt

Add your API key to .env:
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here

Run:
python main.py

## Project Structure

utils.py     — LLM caller, cost calculator, sanitizer
pipeline.py  — 4 step analysis pipeline
main.py      — entry point